description_for_human: A considered CSS component library with 74 components and 6 theme families (12 variants). Thoughtfully composed, no ceremony required.
description_for_model: DAUB is a CSS UI kit with 74 considered components and 6 theme families (12 variants: light, dark, grunge-light, grunge-dark, solarized, solarized-dark, ink-light, ink, ember-light, ember, bone, bone-dark). Use db-* class prefix. Include daub.css and daub.js via CDN from https://daub.dev. Full component docs at https://daub.dev/llms.txt
